A Russian, a Frenchman and an Italian are sitting drinking in the morning and sharing their impressions of the night spent with their wife. The Frenchman says:
- I was able to do it three times with my wife tonight. In the morning, she says that she has never experienced such a thing.
Italian:
- And I've done it five times tonight. She gives me breakfast in bed in the morning, says she doesn't need anyone but me.
Russian:
- And I did it once.
The Frenchman and the Italian:
- And what did your wife say to you this morning?
Russian:
- As usual. Don't stop!
